items.description:
Https and SSL secure the data sent between a server and a user. 

Thanks to free SSL certificates by [LetsEncrypt](https://letsencrypt.org/
) and Google's push to make https the default for every domain through [Chrome](https://security.googleblog.com/2016/09/moving-towards-more-secure-web.html) a huge [jump](https://letsencrypt.org/stats/) in adoption occurred.
